Package: suggestK
Type: Package
Title: Crawl and Visulaize Related Search Terms from the Major Search Engines; Google, Naver, and Daum.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Victor Lee
Maintainer: The package maintainer <kwangchun.lee.7@gmail.com>
Description: This package aims to crawl related search terms from the major search engines. 
    Because the major search engines in Korea have different interfaces, 
    each has its own crawling functions.
    The crawling function returns dataframe suitable for network visualizaion.
    Based on the tidy dataframe, it supports the netowrk visualization 
    and interactive drilldown of search terms.
License: MIT
Depends: tidyverse, networkD3, igraph, glue, urltools, rvest, qdapTools, httr, networkD3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: tidyverse
